Package: wlanpi-persistent-identity
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Maintains persistent system identity across A/B partition switches
 Preserves SSH host keys and machine-id to prevent "host identification changed"
 warnings and ensure consistent DHCP leases and network profiles when switching
 between root partitions.